{"tid":1323314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"now:六月內地訪港旅行團未因修例爭議減少","createTime":"2019-07-16T08:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T08:05:20.000Z","uid":267309,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c98dc870dff992c81ed77a7127ec4e8f1d94d8","tid":1323314,"uid":267309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355576&amp;fbclid=IwAR209A9Xt1jUOra3kGl0cW4oo6-os3Nwqqp2jxwWzqMxwg19gwQPMMoDdAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355576%26fbclid%3DIwAR209A9Xt1jUOra3kGl0cW4oo6-os3Nwqqp2jxwWzqMxwg19gwQPMMoDdAs&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTef1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=211e7911\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355576%26fbclid%3DIwAR209A9Xt1jUOra3kGl0cW4oo6-os3Nwqqp2jxwWzqMxwg19gwQPMMoDdAs&h=78ada6a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355576&amp;fbclid=IwAR209A9Xt1jUOra3kGl0cW4oo6-os3Nwqqp2jxwWzqMxwg19gwQPMMoDdAs</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】旅遊業議會表示，上月內地訪港旅行團的數字，未有因為逃犯條例修訂爭議而減少。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會回覆本台查詢時指，今年六月有5641個內地旅行團來港，比去年六月增加約兩成三，至於今年上半年，一共有39332團來港，較去年同期上升約三成四。議會仍在統計七月初的數據，暫時未能提供。"},{"pid":"320fb952a62a4543fe59741d01e15e8f08d41f82","tid":1323314,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b596a3e6cf780841269a71c7e50135967bd625","tid":1323314,"uid":4811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"咁撚賤嘅？屌極都要死落嚟"},{"pid":"148c798b4ae1afd53d2c18fb76beedcd11ea3bfe","tid":1323314,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c98dc870dff992c81ed77a7127ec4e8f1d94d8","tid":1323314,"uid":267309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.